Title: miR-1-transfected poly(A)-selected RNA-seq
Extraction_Protocol: mRNA-seq: Total mRNA was either depleted of tRNAs/rRNAs or used for poly(A)-selection. In both cases, the RNA was randomly fragmented by partial alkaline hydrolysis and then size-selected RNA fragments (25-45 nt) were used for library preparation. Ribosome profiling: Cell extracts were processed exactly as described in Guo et al., 2010 (GSE22004) Libraries were constructed exactly as described in Guo et al., 2010 (GSE22004)
